---
title: Cheat's Baked Chicken Dhal with Red Lentils & Silverbeet
description: No wonder dhal is the darling of Indian home cooking – it's nutritious, versatile, easy to make and brimming with flavour. Here, we're adding tender pieces of chicken, versatile veggies and crunchy crushed peanuts.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/cheats-baked-chicken-dhal-52b76d64.jpg
